de: Amendment No 2 to the Agreement between the Governement of the Swiss confederation represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs and the Government of the Republic of Uzbekistan represented by the Ministry of Foreign Economic Relations, Investments and Trade on the Granting of Financial Assistance for the Syrdarya Water Supply Project  - 24-09-2019 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO und Usbekistan betreffend  "Syrdarya Water Supply Project"
